Stream API is a way to express and process collections of objects
 Enable us to perform operations like filtering, mapping, reducing and sorting.

 How to creat Stream
 ->>
    Stream<T> stream;
 -->

 The features of JAVA Stream
 1. stream is not a data strcture it just takes input from collections arrays or i/o channels
 2. do not modifiy the original data, only produce results using thier methods
 3. intermediate operations like filter, map ,etc are lazy and return another stream, -> you can chain them together.
 4. a terminal  operations like collect, forEach, count ends the stream and gives final result.


  INPUT --> OPERATION 1 -> operations 2 -> oeprations  .... n -> output

